st personal computers and servers worldwide.", "IBM is an American multinational technology corporation headquartered in Armonk, New York, founded in 1911. It pioneered mainframe computing, created the Watson AI platform, and holds a vast portfolio of technology patents."], "scores": [0.8027525253969019, 0.7128157925513686, 0.6484961223571335, 0.6136872645321472, 0.5980598722658854], "model_name": "bge-base", "document_ids": ["Nvidia", "AMD", "OpenAI", "Intel", "IBM"]}}